Q & A : 
1) What Is Turbo Sim:  www.mwc.my/turbosim
Turbo Sim Is Used To Unlock Imported Apple iPhone Which Has Network Locked (Sim Locked), After Apply the Turbo Sim Sticker, The iPhone Can Used As Normal In Malaysia & International Without Problem.
2) What Is SimFree (No Network Locked):
iPhone Is Originally Unlocked To All Worldwide Network Before Bring Into Malaysia. Therefore Without Putting Turbo Sim Sticker, User Can Use All Sim Card In Malaysia & Oversea Instantly.
3) What Is Japan Set: 
iPhone Is Imported From Japan. 
4) What Is USA Set:
iPhone Is Imported From USA. 
5) What Is The Different Between Japan VS USA Set:
Japan Set While Taking Picture, Camera Shutter Sound Can Not Be Silent Due To Japan Policy. 
USA Set Is Exactly Same As Malaysia Set While Taking Picture Camera Shutter Sound Can Be Mute.
